    <div class="home_copyBlock"><span class="headline">Welcome to Montana Milling, Inc.
      </span>
      <hr />
      <p><p>Our unique advantage is that our mills are located in the heart of the world recognized golden triangle grain producing area of Montana. We specialize in custom milling, meeting each customers special needs and demands. We only offer the highest quality without exception. Our service is superior and consistent. Our grains must meet strict quality tests and standards. They are carefully and naturally processed to retain their pure, wholesome goodness and rich flavor. Every shipment is personally quality checked before leaving our mill.</p>
<p> </p>
